# âš ï¸ IMPORTANT: Typography System Update

**The typography weights have been updated globally.** These changes apply to BOTH the Dashboard and Log tabs. Please update your existing Dashboard components to match.

### Font Weight Changes (Global)

| Element | Old Weight | New Weight |
|---------|------------|------------|
| Body text | 400 | **500** |
| Labels | 500 | **600** |
| Section headers (overline) | 500 | **600** |
| Active tab label | 600 | **700** |
| Inactive tab label | 400 | **500** |
| Icon stroke (active) | 2 | **2.5** |
| Icon stroke (inactive) | 1.5 | **2** |

### Color Updates (Global)

| Token | Old Value | New Value | Reason |
|-------|-----------|-----------|--------|
| textPrimary | #3D352F | **#2D2420** | Better contrast |
| textSecondary | #7A6E66 | **#6B5D54** | Better contrast |
| textTertiary | #A89E96 | **#9A8E86** | Better contrast |

