# Data Model (Log Entry)

```typescript
interface DailyLog {
  id: string;
  userId: string;
  date: string;  // ISO date: "2024-12-25"
  
  // Macros (stored as running totals)
  proteinGrams: number;
  carbsGrams: number;
  fatGrams: number;
  // Calculated: caloriesTotal = (protein * 4) + (carbs * 4) + (fat * 9)
  
  // Body
  sleepHours: number | null;
  weightLbs: number | null;
  
  // Cycle
  isPeriodDay: boolean | null;
  // Calculated server-side from period history:
  // cyclePhase, cycleDay, nextPeriodPrediction
  
  // Activity
  steps: number;  // From HealthKit (V2) or mock (V1)
  
  // Subjective
  energyRating: 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 | null;
  hungerRating: 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 | null;
  motivationRating: 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 | null;
  
  // Metadata
  createdAt: string;
  updatedAt: string;
}

interface CycleInfo {
  phase: 'menstrual' | 'follicular' | 'ovulation' | 'luteal';
  cycleDay: number;
  nextPeriodIn: number;  // Days until predicted next period
}
```

---

# API Endpoints (Suggested)

```
GET    /api/log/:date          â†’ Get log for specific date
POST   /api/log/:date          â†’ Create/update log for date
PATCH  /api/log/:date/macros   â†’ Add macro entry (increments totals)
PATCH  /api/log/:date/rating   â†’ Save single rating
GET    /api/cycle/current      â†’ Get calculated cycle info
```

